channel.title: Looking for other players
channel.description:
Hello I am looking for a few other people to go dungeoneering with me tonight for about 1 or 2 hours or maybe even longer. It's probably recommended you be around 160 combat as I will be hosting the party. This isn't a rush thing as I plan on killing everything in time. I will not tolerate leechers. Get off your bum and work for your levels.
Use friends chat "Altrika"
